# Smart Medical Report Generator - Implementation Plan

## TODO List

- [x] 1. Add Patient Information Form section in index.html
- [x] 2. Add Medical Report container in index.html (hidden by default)
- [x] 3. Add CSS styles for the report in style.css
- [x] 4. Add JavaScript functions for report generation in main.js
- [x] 5. Enhanced clinical interpretation with detailed analysis

## Implementation Details

### HTML Changes (index.html)
- Added Smart Medical Report Generator section with:
  - Patient Information form (Full Name, Age, Gender, Height, Weight)
  - ECG Measurement input fields (Heart Rate, PR Interval, QRS Duration, QT Interval, Electrical Axis)
  - Generate Medical Report button
  - Medical Report container with professional hospital-style layout

### CSS Changes (style.css)
- Added comprehensive styles for:
  - Patient form card with modern design
  - Medical report container with white background
  - Report sections (Patient Info, ECG Measurements, Interpretation, BMI Analysis, Clinical Insight, Summary)
  - Status badges for normal/abnormal/warning states
  - Print styles for PDF export

### JavaScript Changes (main.js)
- Enhanced generateMedicalReport() function with:
  - Direct ECG input field support
  - Detailed clinical interpretation for all ECG parameters
  - Comprehensive BMI analysis with WHO classification
  - Clinical insight generation based on cardiac and BMI findings
  - Medical summary with findings summary

### Clinical Interpretation Features
- Heart Rate: Bradycardia, Normal, Tachycardia with causes
- PR Interval: Short, Normal, Prolonged with clinical significance
- QRS Duration: Normal, Bundle Branch Block detection
- QT Interval: Short, Normal, Prolonged with arrhythmia risk
- Electrical Axis: Normal, LAD, RAD, Extreme with clinical context
- BMI: Underweight, Normal, Overweight, Obese with health recommendations
